OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, About 300 Sunday train services across 
OL,6, Scotland have been cancelled due to a  
OL,7, shortage of drivers linked to an       
OL,8, ongoing pay dispute.                   
OL,10,FScotRail, which was nationalised last  
OL,11,Fmonth, has apologised to customers for 
OL,12,Fthe disruption, which comes on the day 
OL,13,Fits new timetable is launched.         
OL,15,FLast weekend driver shortages affected 
OL,16,F110 services.                          
OL,18,FBut since then Aslef has balloted its  
OL,19,Fmembers for strike action after        
OL,20,Frejecting a 2.2% pay offer.            
